{"article_id":"pYGFpIghfWzbv3F7","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Trump thanks Kim Jong Un","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"as he welcomes home detainees from North Korea","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"The president also jokes","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"that the event 'probably broke the all time in history television rating for three o ' clock in the morning . '","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"President Donald Trump welcomed home three Americans","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"formerly imprisoned by North Korea on Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"greeting them in a dramatic scene","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that played out in the early morning hours on the tarmac at Joint Base Andrews .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"The three released prisoners landed Thursday at the Maryland military facility , the home base for Air Force One , at 2:42 a.m. ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"where they were greeted by President Donald Trump , Vice President Mike Pence and their respective wives .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Secretary of State Mike Pompeo ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"who had secured the release of the men on a Wednesday trip to North Korea","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"and arrived at Andrews minutes earlier on his own plane ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"also greeted the men .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"\" We want to thank Kim Jong Un , \"","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"after emerging from the medical plane","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that transported the three prisoners ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"which he and his wife had boarded","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"to greet the men .","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"\" We very much appreciate","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"that he allowed them to go before the meeting .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"He was nice","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"in letting them go before the meeting ...","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"That was a big thing , very important to me . \"","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Andrews was decorated for the occasion with a massive American flag","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"hanging from the ladders of two fire trucks .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Trump joked with reporters","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that the event \" probably broke the all time in history television rating for three o ' clock in the morning . \"","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"After arriving ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"the prisoners were taken to Walter Reed National Military Medical Center in Bethesda , Maryland , for further evaluation and medical treatment .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"The three men are Korean-Americans Kim Dong Chul , Kim Sang-duk","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"( also known as Tony Kim ) ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"and Kim Hak-song .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"North Korea accused them of anti-state activities .","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"Breaking News Alerts","depth":3},{"id":36,"text":"Get breaking news","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"when it happens -","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"in your inbox .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"By signing up","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Pompeo ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"who flew the three prisoners out of North Korea on his plane Wednesday to Yokota Air Base outside Tokyo ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"told reporters then","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"that the three men were in good health","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"considering what they had been through","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"and had been able to board the plane in Pyongyang","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"without assistance .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"In Japan , the former detainees boarded a separate plane","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"that offered better medical facilities ,","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"trailing Pompeo first to Anchorage , Alaska ,","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"for refueling","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"and then to Andrews .","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"The release is seen as a further sign of thawing relations between the U.S. and North Korea ,","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"after Kim last month pledged to suspend missile tests and close a nuclear test site .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"But it also comes amid renewed uncertainty","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"around how the summit will pan out , after Trump ' s decision earlier this week","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"to pull out of the Iran nuclear deal .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Pompeo ' s trip to Pyongyang was scheduled to coincide with the president ' s decision","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"to remove the U.S. from the Iran agreement , a move","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"intended to signal progress on one foreign policy front","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"even as the administration withdrew from one of the signature diplomatic deals","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"struck by former President Barack Obama .","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"Plans for a meeting between Trump and Kim mark a dramatic shift in the relationship between the two men ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"who spent weeks last summer hurling threats and insults at one another across the Pacific Ocean .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"A meeting between a sitting U.S. president and the leader of North Korea would be a historic first ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"and Pompeo ' s first visit to North Korea over Easter weekend marked the first known meeting between a U.S. official and a North Korean leader","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"since then-Secretary of State Madeleine Albright met with Kim Jong Il , Kim Jong Un ' s father , in 2000 .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"\" My proudest achievement will be when we denuclearize that entire peninsula , \"","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"\" This is what people have been waiting a long time for .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"I ' m very honored to free the three folks .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"The true honor is going to be","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"if we have a victory","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"in getting rid of nuclear weapons . \"","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Trump predicted","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"that his planned meeting with Kim would be \" a very big success \"","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"and suggested","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that his relationship with the North Korean leader is \" starting off on a new footing. \"","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Asked if he might visit North Korea ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"Trump responded","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"\" it could happen . \"","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"\" I really think","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"he wants to do something .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"I think","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"he did this","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"because I really think","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"he wants to do something","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"and bring that country into the real world .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"I really believe that , \"","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"The ex-detainees thanked Trump","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"for securing their freedom","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"in a statement","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"released by the State Department on their behalf","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"and one spoke briefly with reporters through a translator .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"The man said","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"the three prisoners \" were treated in many different ways \"","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"and that he had been forced to do hard labor","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"but also received medical treatment","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"when he was sick .","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"Their release ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"is \" like a dream","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"we are very , very happy , \"","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"\" We would like to express our deep appreciation to the United States government , President Trump , Secretary Pompeo , and the people of the United States","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"for bringing us home , \"","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"the former prisoners said in their statement .","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"\" We thank God , and all our families and friends","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"who prayed for us and for our return .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"God Bless America , the greatest nation in the world . \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":231,"left":160,"right":230,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":150,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":119,"right":149,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":117,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":139,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":128,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":122,"right":127,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":120,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":123,"right":126,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":125,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":10,"right":124,"relation":"elab